<lb ed="ZW" n="0184a15"/><p xml:id="pZW05p0184a1501" style="margin-left:10em">—墓地觀二—</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0184a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">墓地觀三</cb:mulu>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0184a17"/><p xml:id="pZW05p0184a1701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">１１、復次，諸比丘啊！彼於塚間，觀見腐屍，祇有骸
